<doc id="411048" wikidata="Q1171612" url="?curid=411048" title="Fort Wayne (disambiguation)">
<text>Fort Wayne is the second-largest city in the U.S. state of Indiana.

Fort Wayne may also refer to:
*Fort Wayne (fort), the fort which gave its name to the city of Fort Wayne
*Fort Wayne (Detroit), a fort in Michigan
*Fort Wayne (Indian Territory), two early frontier army forts in Indian Territory (now Oklahoma)
**Battle of Old Fort Wayne
*USS &quot;Fort Wayne&quot;, a United States Navy transport during World War I
*Purdue Fort Wayne Mastodons, the athletic program of Purdue University Fort Wayne</text><links>
