* Lawrence, Albert. &quot;Herbert Brownell, Jr.: The &#x27;Hidden Hand&#x27; 1 in the Selection of Earl Warren and the Government&#x27;s Role in Brown v. Board of Education.&quot; &quot;Journal of Supreme Court History&quot; 37.1 (2012): 75–92.

